Usage:  transaction get 
                          [--port INT]
                          WALLET_ID
                          TRANSACTION_ID
                          [--simple-metadata]

  Get a transaction with specified id.

Available options:
  -h,--help                Show this help text
  --port INT               port used for serving the wallet API.
                           (default: 8090)
  --simple-metadata        output metadata json in no-schema
                           encoding
